        "synopsis": {
            "value": "\"Samee Ngoen Phon\" tells the story of Sattawat, a doctor who enters into an artificial marriage to pay off his debts, but another fact is that he actually falls in love with Anussaniya. However, for Anssaniya this marriage was done because it wanted to stop the impossible relationship between her and her uncle-in-law.\n\nAt first the marriage happened normally, without any taste and felt very simple. But without anyone knowing that Sattawat\n\nwas really in love with Anussaniya and found it very difficult to resist the feeling, it became as normal as it was at the beginning of the marriage.",
